                },
                {
                    "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/comment\/23729",
                    "author": {
                        "self": "http:\/\/fw02.zend.com\/issues\/rest\/api\/latest\/user?username=doctorrock83",
                        "name": "doctorrock83",
                        "displayName": "julien PAULI",
                        "active": true
                    },
                    "body": "I agree.\n\nSee that PHP definitly lacks of  \"Package\" visibility :-(\nThat visibility could be used in helpers to get the broker instance back from the actioncontroller , but this same one could'nt be available out of the Zend_Controller scope ( aka, not public ).\n\nPackage visibility would also be very usefull in many other situations, particulary in Zend_Controller package.\n\n",
